    "name": "Dark Age Asunder",
    "steam_appid": 3200770,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200770/extras/a8d4c046c564b25faa9ac3568c0d33f8.avif?t=1752730755\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200770/extras_big/a8d4c046c564b25faa9ac3568c0d33f8.avif?t=1752730755 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Dark Age Asunder</i> is an action rogue-lite bullet heaven where you battle through endless waves of monsters while rebuilding a fallen kingdom. Choose your hero, unlock powerful abilities, gather resources, and restore what was lost - one run at a time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world lies in ruins. An evil King and his dark Wizard have razed villages and unleashed relentless monsters upon the land. It’s up to a group of heroes to reclaim the realm by fighting back, rebuilding settlements, and growing strong enough to dethrone the tyrant.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Select Your Hero!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Dark Age Asunder </i>is a <strong>rogue-lite bullet heaven</strong> game. Your character will automatically attack in the direction they are facing. Each character has a different playstyle, allowing you to choose one that fits your preference. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200770/extras/fa698356eff8030c048538e9c70f157f.poster.avif?t=1752730755\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200770/extras/fa698356eff8030c048538e9c70f157f.webm?t=1752730755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200770/extras/fa698356eff8030c048538e9c70f157f.mp4?t=1752730755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Level Up!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you go through each level, a different type of enemy will spawn each minute. Enemies drop <strong>EXP, </strong>or <strong>potions</strong> with temporary effects. When you collect enough EXP, you can select one of three <strong>upgrades</strong> to give your character additional abilities or to strengthen their stats for this run only.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200770/extras/5f1c8682be3066b74fbc7426ab909582.poster.avif?t=1752730755\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200770/extras/5f1c8682be3066b74fbc7426ab909582.webm?t=1752730755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200770/extras/5f1c8682be3066b74fbc7426ab909582.mp4?t=1752730755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gather Resources to rebuild your home!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stand within the bounds of a <strong>Resource Discovery</strong> to claim them. The resources available to capture are <strong>Wood, Iron, Mana, </strong>and <strong>Gold. </strong>Every minute that passes, you receive resources for each <strong>Iron Mine, Gold Mine, </strong>and <strong>Mana Well</strong> Resource Discovery you have claimed. <strong>Wood </strong>is a finite resource and can only be obtained once per Resource Discovery. These resources can be used to build <strong>Structures</strong> that will help you on your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200770/extras/d8838157abafb99b3ec6dcdaeeb6790f.poster.avif?t=1752730755\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200770/extras/d8838157abafb99b3ec6dcdaeeb6790f.webm?t=1752730755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200770/extras/d8838157abafb99b3ec6dcdaeeb6790f.mp4?t=1752730755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Come Back Stronger!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After finishing or dying during a level, you have the ability to <strong>Upgrade </strong>your character’s stats permanently in the shop using Gold you have collected while playing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200770/extras/56703e621e757dd7ceea9549da0c6374.poster.avif?t=1752730755\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200770/extras/56703e621e757dd7ceea9549da0c6374.webm?t=1752730755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200770/extras/56703e621e757dd7ceea9549da0c6374.mp4?t=1752730755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
